                "value": "Choose a space within 6 spaces. A circle of mushrooms appears with a radius of 1 space, centered on the chosen space. Any creature within the fairy ring can reroll rolls from potions and healing spells. The fairy ring lasts for 1 day. When you cast fairy ring, any active fairy ring spells are ended. Any creature that can take a major action to destroy the fair ring.",
